<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٨٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4563">عَلِيُّ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6257">مُعْتَمِرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2609">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَمْ يَبْقَ مِمَّنْ صَلَّى الْقِبْلَتَيْنِ غَيْرِي»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>